      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in true mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless original paint to the pristine leather interior, has been preserved with the utmost care. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as intended and a complete service history to verify its maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner.",
