    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely pristine! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. If you're looking for a total gem that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out!",
      "price": 44900.0,
