    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving, naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8. It maintains a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline with documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast shifts, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal power delivery across the rear axle. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system and factory-spec bushings. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the stainless steel exhaust system, reflects a meticulous maintenance history. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with zero deferred maintenance and a flawless powertrain.",
